item.title: Initial Post
item.description: Welcome to my blog! I plan to use this site to share my projects and code with the world, and may occasionally speak to other interests of mine.

item.title: About Me
item.description: I am an undergraduate computer science student at the University of Notre Dame graduating in 2022. Outside of my studies I spend much of my time at the pool playing for the Notre Dame men’s water polo team. Originally, I am from the Bellevue/Eastside area of Seattle, where I attended Eastside Catholic School and graduated in 2018. I am also a proud alumni of the Bellevue Club Swim Team, where I swam since 9 years old until I graduated high school.

item.title: Contact Me
item.description: Get In Touch Feel free to get in touch with me! Email: dwilli36@nd.edu Recruiters If you are a recruiter/employer, you can view my resume at this github repo, where appropriate contact information is available.
